=head1 DESCRIPTION

Additional tax information associated with your TRN in Poland.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 IndividualRegistrationNumber => Str

The individual tax registration number (NIP). Individual NIP is valid
for other taxes excluding VAT purposes.


=head2 IsGroupVatEnabled => Bool

True if your business is a member of a VAT group with a NIP active for
VAT purposes. Otherwise, this is false.



